          "id": "medmcqa-9b67ab79-55ec-4005-91e0-9874ad934308",
          "text": "A 60-year-old male, chronic smoker, presented with fatigue and chest pain. On examination, there was inset left eyeball with drooping upper left eyelid and reduced left pupil size. Which of the following is the most likely diagnosis in this condition?",
