          "id": "medmcqa-b25e95f0-40e7-4b5a-aa94-55a547d5ca1f",
          "text": "In a study of lifestyle influences on health, investigators observe that sending children outside to play instead of letting them sit for hours in front of the television can have long-term health benefits. Which of the following tissues is most likely to be in better condition by middle age from this lifestyle change?",
