          "explanation": "The peripheral blood picture of this patient is quite characteristic of chronic myeloid leukemia.\nChronic  myeloid  leukemia  is  a  stem  cell  disease  that  is  characterized  by  leukocytosis  with  granulocytic  immaturities,  basophilia, splenomegaly and distinct chromosomal abnormality Philadelphia chromosome."
