          "text": "A 2-year-old boy is brought in by his mother because of the bloody stool after ingestion of unknown amount of rat poison (coumarin based). He is admitted and treated with fresh frozen plasma and vitamin K after his prothrombin time (PT) was found to be prolonged. What is the reason for bloody stool in this case?",
